In my case it was caused by missing empty constructor for *Property classes.
After some tests I use bellow Proguard configuration but I think it's still not optimal.
```
HoloEverywhere
-keep,allowoptimization class com.WazaBe.HoloEverywhere. { 
    public ;
    protected ;
}
-keep,allowoptimization interface com.WazaBe.HoloEverywhere. { ; }
```
. In my case it was caused by missing empty constructor for Property classes.
After some tests I use bellow Proguard configuration but I think it's still not optimal.
```
HoloEverywhere
-keep,allowoptimization class com.WazaBe.HoloEverywhere. { 
    public ;
    protected ;
}
-keep,allowoptimization interface com.WazaBe.HoloEverywhere. { *; }
```
